<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/603> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #603" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Liv. 6.42.4; Fast. Cap. ([- -Cincin]natus Capitolinus); Degrassi 32f., 104, 398f. On Poenus, see Lübker no. 6." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/601> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #601" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "In Livy the name is T. Quinctius Poenus, while in Fast. Cap. the part preserved ([...Cincin]natus Capitolinus) clearly indicates the name above. Perhaps Livy identified him with the Dictator of 361." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/592> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #592" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Liv. 6.38.2; Diod. 15.78.1; Fast. Cap. ([- -C]apitolin.; [- -M]alugin. VII; [- -Praet]extat. IIII; the rest entire); Chr. 354 (Capitolino et Structo); Degrassi 32f., 103f., 398f." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/591> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #591" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/4> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Diod. names only three Military Tribunes in this year, the first three in the list above. On the name of Quinctius, see also Fast. Cap. on 367." .
